         <td colspan="2" style="border-top:2px solid #336699"> <a name="came-from"><h1>Came From</h1></a> <img src="http://old.statcounter.com/images/features/camefrom.gif" alt="Came From" class="image_border" border="3" width="500" height="190"> <br><br> This is one of the most important stats for any webmaster. This tool allows you to see how your visitors are finding your site, and where they are coming from. This can help you identify, for example, links on other sites that are working and those that aren't, and help you trace where people are referring to your website. <br><br> </td> 
        </tr> 
